com.aionemu.gameserver.dataholders
Class DataManager

java.lang.Object
  com.aionemu.gameserver.dataholders.DataManager

public final class DataManager
extends java.lang.Object

This class is holding whole static data, that is loaded from /data/static_data directory.
The data is loaded by XMLDataLoader using JAXB.

This class temporarily also contains data loaded from txt files by DataLoaders. It'll be changed later.

Author:
Luno , orz
